  <description type="morphology">Plants 5–45 cm. Stems (peduncles) sometimes with 1–3, leafy bracts proximally. Leaves: blades linear to linear-lanceolate, 7–30 cm, margins entire, often undulate, often ciliolate, (apices acuminate) faces glabrous or villous. Involucres 14–30 mm. Phyllaries 8–25, green to minutely purple-dotted, often with purple-lined midnerves, lanceolate, (apices acuminate) faces glabrous or villous, especially on margins and midribs. Florets 13–90; ligules 10–25 mm. Cypselae light brown or gray, 7–13 mm, sometimes narrowed distally, not beaked; pappi of 10–30, aristate scales 10–17 mm. 2n = 18.</description>
